{"datasourceType":"Kusto","cluster":"lens.kusto.windows.net","database":"Sandbox","query":"let BladeLoadTime =
cluster("Azportalpartner").database("AzurePortal").ClientTelemetry
| where PreciseTimeStamp >= startofday(ago(14d)) and PreciseTimeStamp <= ago(0d)
| where action == "BladeFullReady"
| where name contains "Microsoft_Azure_Monitoring"
| where name contains 'InfraInsightsMultiAksClusterInsightsFrameBlade'
| where actionModifier == 'complete'
| extend OpenedBy = tostring(todynamic(data).openedByBladeName) 
| summarize Users = dcount(userId, 2), Loads = count(), percentiles(duration, 50, 80, 90, 95, 99) by name, bin(PreciseTimeStamp, 1d)
//| order by name, IncludesExtensionLoadTime
| order by PreciseTimeStamp asc 
| project PreciseTimeStamp, P95 = percentile_duration_95, name;
BladeLoadTime
| union (
 cluster("Azportalpartner").database("AzurePortal").ExtTelemetry
| where PreciseTimeStamp >= startofday(ago(14d)) and PreciseTimeStamp <= ago(0d)
| where source =~ "AzureMonitor/Containers" 
| where action =~ "getClustersFromBackend"
| where actionModifier =~ "Complete"
| extend name = "getClustersArgQuery"
|summarize P95 = percentile(duration, 95) by bin(PreciseTimeStamp, 1d), name
)
| render timechart
